x10.matrix.block

Class DenseBlockMatrix

  • x10.matrix.Matrix
    • x10.matrix.block.DenseBlockMatrix

  • public class DenseBlockMatrix
extends Matrix
    OBSOLETE. Use BlockMatrix. Dense block matrix is constructed by using an array or dense blocks, and grid partition specifies how each block is mapped to the overall dense matrix.
